data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath home in Orlando  in the greater central location,*** Location location location***  This beautiful large lot home has a wonderful  setting when you walk into the living room area and then you have the kitchen to the left where you can cook in peace, followed by the nook area and the outside  glassed window patio which takes you out to the large pool area, if you would go right when you first walk in home you will be in where the four rooms sits with master bedroom on the far right, which now has a back entryway, this homw also comes with a large two car garage and three to four car parking drive way depending on your car size. New roof in 2022, new kitchen update cabinets and counter tops, new outside garage  sink added, new lighting fixtures and fans, in 2022, 2024 master bed room floor update and new master bedroom entry door added, with a large pool,  larger pie shape lot with beautiful fruit trees and more. Solar was added 193.25 a month will be assumption over when purchase of home right now her electric bill shows a -84 dollar balance due to the savings. Next to seaworld, universal and disney is near by, lots of shopping centers near by and more. Hunters creek is very close and sandlake and IDrive.
